[mahina at nakakatakot na musika]

44:12.304 --> 44:13.720
[bumuntong-hininga]

44:18.517 --> 44:22.660
-[nanginig na hininga]

44:24.765 --> 44:28.424
[nakakapangilabot na musika]

44:29.770 --> 44:32.808
Hindi, hindi,
hindi, hindi, hindi, hindi.

